ice+against+the+worshipping+of+God.+They+forbid+idolatry%2C+apostasy%2C+heresy%2C+superstition%2C+perjury%2C+blasphemy%2C+and+move+us+to+the+pure+and+true+worshipping+of+God+in+heart%2C+word+and+deed.+In+the+Second+table+be+seven+Commandments%2C+which+command+us+to+give+reverence+and+honor+to+every+man+in+his+degree%2C+to+profit+all%2C+and+hurt+none%3A+to+do+unto+others%2C+as+we+would+be+done+to+ourselves.%22%29&amp;rft.place=Manchester%2C+England&amp;rft.pub=The+Chetham+Society&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aloha.net%2F%7Emikesch%2Fvaux.htm%2348&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Golden_Rule"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
