<li id="cite_note-SiM_.26_W_.26_R_.26_D-52"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-SiM_.26_W_.26_R_.26_D_52-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-SiM_.26_W_.26_R_.26_D_52-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-SiM_.26_W_.26_R_.26_D_52-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">[English Title: Conversations of Muhammad]<br />
