<li id="cite_note-64"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-64">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a href="/wiki/L._Ron_Hubbard" title="L. Ron Hubbard">Hubbard, L. Ron</a> (2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.thewaytohappiness.org/thewaytohappiness/precepts/try-to-treat-others-as-you-would-want-them-to-treat-you.html">"Precept 20"</a>. <i>The Way to Happiness</i>. The Way to Happiness Foundation International<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.thewaytohappiness.org/thewaytohappiness/precepts/try-to-treat-others-as-you-would-want-them-to-treat-you.html">http://www.thewaytohappiness.org/thewaytohappiness/precepts/try-to-treat-others-as-you-would-want-them-to-treat-you.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 22 April 2012</span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Precept+20&amp;rft.atitle=The+Way+to+Happiness&amp;rft.aulast=Hubbard%2C+L.+Ron&amp;rft.au=Hubbard%2C+L.+Ron&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.pub=The+Way+to+Happiness+Foundation+International&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewaytohappiness.org%2Fthewaytohappiness%2Fprecepts%2Ftry-to-treat-others-as-you-would-want-them-to-treat-you.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Golden_Rule"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
